        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End the Threat of Default Act of 2024&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill repeals the statutory debt limit. (The debt limit is the amount of money that the Department of the Treasury may borrow to fund federal operations.)&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
